abstract: >-
  A typology for the missing half of the AI agent landscape: production
  agents change the state of the world; consumption agents change your
  interface to it. States the three-test/four-trait criterion, an
  eighty-year lineage, the empirical base, a risk register with eight
  red lines, and a research agenda.
